sentences: Ciney Gurung (Nepali: सिने गुरुङ) is a singer, composer, and songwriter originally from Kurseong, Darjeeling and lives in Nepal now.
In 2009, Radio Kantipur named Gurung the best female pop singer of the year.
Gurung married musician, Rojesh Shrestha, in 2005 and they have a daughter together.
